  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/a700ca5bd0d1b41a610b60fa372120b8.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/a700ca5bd0d1b41a610b60fa372120b8.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who will reign supreme in your household?  </strong>Gather up to 4 players for the ultimate couch play experience. House of Golf 2 is tailor-made for lively gatherings and family fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/bc6b819ddd327cc8fa4f57003edc8b19.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/bc6b819ddd327cc8fa4f57003edc8b19.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span>Over 100 meticulously crafted holes to conquer, new holes unlocked by Live Tournament and Events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/27dedfce9c5dc2335628637358d92159.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/27dedfce9c5dc2335628637358d92159.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span><strong> </strong>Unleash your creativity and skill with our innovative Trick Score System. Showcase your mastery with jaw-dropping shots, ricocheting around corners and defying gravity to earn impressive scores and wow your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/5c8b20399435dba146080b8a64f0900c.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/5c8b20399435dba146080b8a64f0900c.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mettle? Dive into Live Tournaments and compete on dynamic courses for exciting prizes—from coins to exclusive skins and golf balls. There's always a new challenge to conquer and rewards to claim. Don’t miss out—grab your virtual clubs and make your mark...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We'll see you on the Leaderboards!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/a700ca5bd0d1b41a610b60fa372120b8.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/a700ca5bd0d1b41a610b60fa372120b8.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who will reign supreme in your household?  </strong>Gather up to 4 players for the ultimate couch play experience. House of Golf 2 is tailor-made for lively gatherings and family fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/bc6b819ddd327cc8fa4f57003edc8b19.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/bc6b819ddd327cc8fa4f57003edc8b19.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span>Over 100 meticulously crafted holes to conquer, new holes unlocked by Live Tournament and Events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/27dedfce9c5dc2335628637358d92159.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/27dedfce9c5dc2335628637358d92159.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span><strong> </strong>Unleash your creativity and skill with our innovative Trick Score System. Showcase your mastery with jaw-dropping shots, ricocheting around corners and defying gravity to earn impressive scores and wow your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras/5c8b20399435dba146080b8a64f0900c.avif?t=1761929813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914390/extras_big/5c8b20399435dba146080b8a64f0900c.avif?t=1761929813 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mettle? Dive into Live Tournaments and compete on dynamic courses for exciting prizes—from coins to exclusive skins and golf balls. There's always a new challenge to conquer and rewards to claim. Don’t miss out—grab your virtual clubs and make your mark...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We'll see you on the Leaderboards!</strong></p>",
